sudo apt install python-pip
sudo apt install python3-pip
sudo pip install youtube-dl

This is how to download a video from youtube.com
youtube-dl -F   https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kOFu6b3w6c0 --no-check-certificate
choose the video you want
youtube-dl -f 18  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kOFu6b3w6c0 --no-check-certificate

Convert an *.mp4 to *.mp3
ffmpeg -i video.mp4 audio.mp3

Convert *.mp4 to image  
ffmpeg -i Beatles-YellowSubmarine.mp4 -vf fps=30 out%d.png
